### Genfeed API - Organizations Relationships Endpoints
### Get organization brands, analytics, ingredients, videos, tags, posts, activities, tasks
### Protected by RolesGuard

########################################
# Organization Brands
########################################

### Get Organization Brands
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/brands
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Organization Brands with Pagination
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/brands?page=1&limit=10&sort=-createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


########################################
# Organization Analytics
########################################

### Get Organization Analytics
# Requires: superadmin, owner, admin, creator, or analytics role
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Organization Analytics with Date Range
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/analytics?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-02-15&brandId={{testBrandId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Analytics Time Series
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/analytics/timeseries
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Analytics Time Series with Filters
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/analytics/timeseries?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-02-15&groupBy=day&brandId={{testBrandId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Analytics Platforms
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/analytics/platforms
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Analytics Platforms with Date Range
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/analytics/platforms?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-02-15&brandId={{testBrandId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Platform-Specific Analytics
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/platforms/twitter/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Platform-Specific Analytics with Filters
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/platforms/instagram/analytics?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-02-15&brandId={{testBrandId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Top Content Analytics
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/analytics/top-content?metric=views&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Top Content with Full Filters
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/analytics/top-content?metric=likes&limit=20&startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-02-15&brandId={{testBrandId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


########################################
# Organization Collections
########################################

### Get Organization Ingredients
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/ingredients
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Organization Ingredients with Filters
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/ingredients?category=image&brand={{testBrandId}}&search=sunset&page=1&limit=20&sort=-createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Organization Videos
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/videos
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Organization Videos with Pagination
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/videos?page=1&limit=20&sort=-createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Organization Tags
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Organization Tags with Pagination
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/tags?page=1&limit=50&sort=label
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Organization Posts
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Organization Posts with Filters
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/posts?platform=twitter&status=scheduled&page=1&limit=20&sort=-scheduledDate
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Organization Activities
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Organization Activities with Pagination
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/activities?page=1&limit=20&sort=-createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Organization Tasks
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Organization Tasks with Pagination
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/tasks?page=1&limit=20&sort=-createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


########################################
# Test Cases
########################################

### Test: Invalid Organization ID
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/invalid-id/brands
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Test: Organization Not Found
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/brands
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Test: Unauthorized Access
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/organizations/{{testOrganizationId}}/brands
